The weekly hours of work Monday to Friday inclusive shall consist of forty (40)
      hours for all employees of Employers covered by this agreement and working on
      a one (1) or two (2) shift operation except as described in Sections 26.02, 26.03,
      26.04, 26.05, 26.06 and 26.07.

The weekly hours of work may be arrived at by having the employees work either:

a. Four (4) consecutive ten-hour shifts, Monday to Thursday or;

b. Four (4) consecutive ten-hour shifts, Tuesday to Friday;

c. Five (5) consecutive eight –hour shifts;

